name: #Found
description: @gareth_wild | Found is an assemblage of discarded items collected from the streets, footpaths, hedgerows and beaches around the UK over the course of a year.  Layered evidence of human activity stretching back minutes, hours, days, weeks, years, decades, even centuries. Sometimes worthless rubbish, sometimes valuable.  Exhibited at Microsoft Research European HQ in Cambridge. Photographed by Richard Legge.  High resolution digital scan from large format 5x4 film transparency. Buyers can also download a high resolution print file.
